== Introduction ==
An [[adobe]] [[rocket stoves|rocket stove]] cooks many of the meals at [[Rancho Mastatal]]. The rocket stove was built using the [[justa stove]] design. Rocket stoves are [[improved cookstoves]] that usually use fuel more efficiently and produce less emissions than a [[Three stone cooking fire|three stone fire]].

